        "body": "This would unfortunately be a breaking change. However, we could start by issuing a warning. For example:\r\n\r\n```python\r\n>>> import dask.array as da\r\n>>> da.eye(3, chunks=2).shape\r\n(3, 3)\r\n>>> da.eye(3, 2).shape\r\n/Users/tom/projects-workspace/dask/dask/array/creation.py:544: FutureWarning: The `chunks` parameter to `eye` should not be specified by position. Please use `chunks=` instead, since the positional order will be changed in a future release to match NumPy.\r\n  warnings.warn(\r\n(3, 3)\r\n```\r\n\r\nSee https://github.com/tomwhite/dask/commit/5738f8d041a89a8f617a742acd27777bde0db197",
